<plot>After a young cop (Stephen Baldwin) gets involved in his third shooting, he is recruited into a special police unit. He quickly learns that the unit is an assassination corps for hoodlums and they don't care who gets in the way. Saving the life of a child gets him a beating by the unit, which they call an initiation. When they raid a mobster's home and start killing hoods and call girls who just happens to be there, he draws a line when he finds one (Tia Carrere) hiding in a closet. He then goes on the run with her with gangsters and the cops both in pursuit.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?479733</url></doc>
